  <brief_title>A Study of Single Doses of ABT-072 in Japanese Healthy Male Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Blinded, Randomized, Placebo-controlled Phase 1 Study in Healthy Male Adults to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetic Profiles of Single Doses of ABT-072</official_title>
