  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the safety, tolerability, and pharmacokinetics of
      blinded, single ascending oral doses of ABT 072 under non-fasting conditions in healthy adult
      Japanese male subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
